    "description": "Texas Instruments India International Enterprises, one of India's leading organizations, is hiring a Backend Developer for our Gurgaon operations. We offer a competitive salary package along with world-class benefits.\n\nAbout Texas Instruments India International Enterprises:\nTexas Instruments India International Enterprises is a leading organization in the Remote sector, committed to excellence, innovation, and employee growth. We offer a dynamic work environment where talent is recognized and rewarded.\n\nKey Responsibilities:\n• Implement new features based on product requirements\n• Optimize application performance and ensure high availability\n• Mentor junior developers and conduct knowledge-sharing sessions\n• Participate in code reviews and contribute to technical discussions\n• Contribute to system architecture and technical design decisions\n• Write clean, maintainable, and well-documented code\n• Integrate third-party APIs and services\n\nRequired Skills & Qualifications:\n• B.Com / M.Com / MBA Finance\n• 10-15 years of relevant experience\n• Proficiency in AWS\n• Proficiency in SQL\n• Proficiency in Node.js\n• Proficiency in CI/CD\n• Proficiency in Kubernetes\n• Proficiency in Docker\n• Proficiency in TypeScript\n• Proficiency in React\n\nWork Mode: Remote - Work from anywhere in India\n\nWhat We Offer:\n• Work-from-home flexibility\n• Transportation and conveyance allowance\n• Competitive salary with performance-linked incentives\n• Comprehensive health insurance for self and family\n• Mobile and internet reimbursement\n• International travel opportunities for senior roles\n• Salary Range: 20 LPA - 40 LPA per annum\n\nLocation: Gurgaon, Haryana, India\n\nIf you are excited about this opportunity, apply now and take the next step in your career journey with Texas Instruments India International Enterprises!",
